implementation.model.spreadsheet

Class SpreadsheetCourseTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • implementation.model.spreadsheet.SpreadsheetCourseTest

  • public class SpreadsheetCourseTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Class SpreadsheetCourseTest is the companion testing class for class model.gradebook.SpreadsheetCourse It implements the following module test plan:

    • Phase 1: Unit test the constructor.

    • Phase 2: Unit test the access methods, getCourseInfo, getCategoryContainer, getStudentRoster, getID, getSettings, getLatePolicy, getGradingDistribution, getStudentRoster, getAddedStudents, isStudentAdded, isStudentDeleted, getStudentsToDelete

    • Phase 3: Unit test the equals method

    • Phase 4: Unit test the constructive methods, addStudent, addStudents, editStudent, deleteStudent, adjustCourseCurve, setCourseInfo, setGradingDistribution, setLatePolicy, setSettings
    Author:
    jamesfazio

      • testSpreadsheetCourse

        public void testSpreadsheetCourse()
                           throws CourseDataException
        Test method for SpreadsheetCourse.SpreadsheetCourse(model.spreadsheet.CourseInfo, model.spreadsheet.GradingScheme, model.spreadsheet.LatePolicy). Construct a SpreadsheetCourse. Ensure that once the SpreadsheetCourse is created that it is not null. If you pass in null CourseInfo into the SpreadsheetCourse, a BadDataException should be thrown. If you pass null grading scheme a CourseDataExcpetion is thrown. 
          Test
  Case    Input                                    Output             Remarks
 =================================================================================
   1      SpreadsheetCourse(info, scheme, policy)  Success
   2      SpreadsheetCourse(info, null, policy)    CourseDataException
   3      SpreadsheetCourse(null, scheme, policy   CourseDataException
        Throws:
        CourseDataException
